🔷 Promises vs Callbacks

| Callbacks     | Promises       |
| ------------- | -------------- |
| Nested code   | Flat structure |
| Hard to read  | Easy to read   |
| Callback hell | Clean chaining |

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Promises vs Async/Await

| Promises         | Async/Await    |
| ---------------- | -------------- |
| Uses .then()     | Uses await     |
| Slightly complex | Cleaner syntax |
| Chain-based      | Sequential     |

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Common Mistakes

❌ Forgetting return in `.then()`
❌ Not handling errors
❌ Nested promises unnecessarily
❌ Ignoring async behavior

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💡 Best Practices

✔ Always use `.catch()`
✔ Return values properly
✔ Keep chain simple
✔ Prefer async/await for readability

